Being a nice person online can make it seem like you're an easy target for other people to be mean to or take advantage of.&#x20;

This doesn't necessarily mean that you don't respect people who are nice, it's just that, for some people, the way they are online is different from how they are in real life. This can also affect how they treat others.

Try to remember that only engage with others in a way that makes you feel protected and respected. If someone is being mean or abusive, and it's affecting you negatively, you might want to consider limiting the interactions that you have with that person.

